<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="home.css">
    <!-- copy this link on every page -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="nav.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Home Page</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="home-container">
        <!-- copy paste this at the top of each ejs route -->
        <nav class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
            <a href="/project" class="nav-link">Project</a>
            <a href="/analysis" class="nav-link">Analysis</a>
        </nav>
        <!-- stop here -->
        <div class="header-container">
            <h1>ChatGPT Efficiency Assignment</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="body-container">
            <h2 class="bios-title"><i>Student Profiles</i></h2>
            <section class="aphy-intro-container">
                <p class="aphy-intro">
                    My name is <a href="https://github.com/aphy18"><b>Aphason Aberham</b></a>. I live in downtown Toronto, and I am currently a third year BCom student, majoring in Information Technology at York University. I have a strong background in HTML, CSS, JavaScript and some of their frameworks, which I've used to develop projects for my portfolio. Notably, I have experience using technologies such as Node.js, Express.js, React.js, PostgresQL, EJS, and jQuery.</p>
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="ayush-intro-container">
                <p class="ayush-intro">
                    I am <a href="https://github.com/imayushhh"><b>Ayush Gupta</b></a>, a student currently pursuing a Bachelor of Arts in Information Technology with a strong interest in cloud computing and full-stack development. I enjoy building interactive applications and exploring ways to integrate AI into real-world solutions. I have a technical background in JavaScript, Python, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, Node.js, and Express.js.
                </p>
            </section>
            <h2 class="about-project-title"><i>About Our Project</i></h2>
            <section class="project-overview">
                <p class="about-project">
                    This application is designed to evaluate ChatGPT’s performance in answering multiple-choice questions across various domains such as History, Social Science, and Computer Security. The app retrieves questions from a MongoDB database, sends them to ChatGPT using the OpenAI API, records the AI’s responses along with response times, and stores the results back into the database. It also includes middleware to validate query inputs, WebSocket integration for live progress updates, and API endpoints to retrieve evaluation metrics in real time. The project demonstrates full-stack development, server-client communication, and the integration of AI-driven evaluation within a web application.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="home-image-container">

            </section>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener('scroll', (e) => {
            const nav = document.querySelector('.nav-container');
            if (window.pageYOffset > 0) {
                nav.classList.add('add-shadow');
            } else {
                nav.classList.remove('add-shadow');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>